            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "Accurate information on the disease , its prevention and treatment can be disseminated through drug information centers ( DICs ) . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "DICs are usually staffed by pharmacists and/or clinical pharmacists / pharmacologists . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 5,
            "text": "DICs are a reliable source of current and unbiased information on COVID-19 and its associated complications ,",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "including management options for healthcare professionals and the public . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
